Package: BLASTr
Title: Parallel taxonomic classification of metabarcoding sequences
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Queiroz", "Lucio Rezende", , "luciorqueiroz@gmail.com", role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6090-1834")),
    person("Heron", "Hilario", , "heronoh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2548-1053"))
  )
Description: Seamlessly run BLAST searches within R, tailored
    for ASV (Amplicon Sequence Variant) analysis.
    This package offers a robust set of functions designed to
    efficiently identify and process sequences from high-throughput
    metagenomicmetagenomic experiments,
    following best practices for sequence data analysis.
